About Me

I have experience building full stack applications with React, ASP.NET for server development, and SQL Server for database design. I have worked in an agile/SCRUM environment where I participated in daily stand-up and frequent code review. I am also familiar in building applications with other Javascript libraries such as JQuery or even vanilla Javascript. I pride myself on having good fundamentals in writing scalable, modularized, and efficient code, always looking for new ways to further my knowledge. Having worked in a team of 15, I thrive well in team settings and am able to adapt and learn quickly.
